{"type":"message","id":"90240b40","parentId":"24dc0d59","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:49:17.330Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-04-14 01:48 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/2). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are senior-frontend. Clone and deploy the full DTLX Frontend system.\n\n## Context\n- Workspace target: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/\n- GitLab: https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend\n- Project ID: 77055851\n- Label: dtlx:deploy-fe\n\n## Steps\n\n### 1. Clone repo if not exists\n- Check if ahv-dtlx-frontend already exists in /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/\n- If NOT exists: git clone https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend.git\n- If exists: cd into it and git pull origin develop\n\n### 2. Setup\n- cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend\n- Check package.json exists\n- Check .env or .env.local\n- yarn install\n\n### 3. Configure API URL\n- Check what API URL the frontend uses (src/services/, src/lib/, .env)\n- Update to point to http://localhost:5555 (DTLX Backend)\n- Check NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL or similar in .env.local\n\n### 4. Build\n- yarn build\n- If build fails: report error and STOP\n\n### 5. Start\n- Start dev server: yarn dev\n- Wait for \"Ready\" or \"started\"\n- Verify: curl http://localhost:3000\n- Report server URL and status\n\n## Rules\n- NEVER push or commit code\n- Read-only setup\n- Keep server RUNNING after setup"}],"timestamp":1776131357287}}
